ng-switch(on="type.value.type")
  div(ng-switch-when="Text")
    h3 Text of any length

    p.
      Add any type of longer form text thatâ€™s written by editors, usually including spaces. 
      Enables you to search for words in the text but not exact matches for the entire text. 
      Use Symbols for short tokens of text like URLs or tags (<a href="http://support.contentful.com/entries/28062416-What-s-the-difference-between-Text-and-Symbol-Fields-">more information</a>).
    ul.u-list
      li Blog post title
      li Product descriptions
      li Article bodies
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/text.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Symbol")
    h3 Short token of text

    p.
      Represent unbreakable and relatively short tokens of text, often made for machine consumption. You can only search for full Symbols, not parts of it like individual words.
    ul.u-list
      li URL
      li Tag
      li Postal code
      li Phone number
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/symbol.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Integer")
    h3 Number without decimals

    p.
      Insert numbers without decimals. Use validations to constrain the range or to only allow specific values.
    ul.u-list
      li Priority
      li Calorie count
      li Age
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/integer.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Number")
    h3 Number with decimals

    p.
      Insert a number with as many decimal figures as needed. Use validations to constrain the ranges or to only allow specific values.
    ul.u-list
      li Weights
      li Temperatures
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/floating.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Boolean")
    h3 Boolean value

    p.
      Insert a boolean value with two choices: either yes or no.
    ul.u-list
      li Open
      li Vegetarian menu
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/boolean.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Date")
    h3 Date with time of day

    p
      | Specify a given date and time. Like the start or end time of an event.
      //- Either the date or the time can be left blank.
    ul.u-list
      li Event start time
      li Holiday date
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/date.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Location")
    h3 Geographical coordinates

    p.
      The latitude and longitude of any place. Locations can be added by entering their coordinates or by searching the location directly on a map.
    ul.u-list
      li Geographical location of a venue
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/location.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Object")
    h3 Embedded JSON object

    p.
      Add an arbitrary JSON structure that you can write and read through the API.
    ul.u-list
      li Custom data from another system
    img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/jsonobject.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Link")
    div(ng-show="type.value.linkType == 'Entry'")
      h3 Link to an Entry
      p.
        Connect your current Entry to another already existing Entry. You can create relationships such as connecting a book to its author.
      ul.u-list
        li Author
        li Category
      img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/linktoentry.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

    div(ng-show="type.value.linkType == 'Asset'")
      h3 Link to an Asset
      p.
        Link a previously uploaded media file to this Entry or add a new one directly when editing.
      ul.u-list
        li Image
        li Attachment
        li Media of any kind
      img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/linktoasset.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

  div(ng-switch-when="Array")
    div(ng-show="type.value.items.type == 'Link' && type.value.items.linkType == 'Entry'")
      h3 Links to multiple Entries
      p.
        Connect your current Entry to other already existing Entries. It works like the individual Entry but it allows you to connect more than one Entry.
      ul.u-list
        li Multiple authors
        li Multiple categories
      img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/linkstoentries.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

    div(ng-show="type.value.items.type == 'Link' && type.value.items.linkType == 'Asset'")
      h3 Links to multiple Assets
      p.
        Link several previously uploaded media files to this Entry or add new ones directly when editing.
      ul.u-list
        li Multiple images
        li Multiple attachments
        li Multiple media files of any kind
      img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/linkstoassets.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")

    div(ng-show="type.value.items.type == 'Symbol'")
      h3 List of multiple Symbols
      p.
        Create a lists of multiple Symbols. It works like an individual Symbol but allows you to add more than one Symbol.
      ul.u-list
        li Multiple tags of a blog post
      img(ng-src="{{::'/app/images/field_type/list.png'|prefixAssetHost}}")
